ib.URM.Instr.T","kind":"ctor","line":49,"name":"Cslib.URM.Instr.T","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.lean#L49-L49"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Instr.S\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">URM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Instr</span>.<span class=\"name\">S</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a> → <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Instr\">Instr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Instr.S","kind":"ctor","line":48,"name":"Cslib.URM.Instr.S","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.lean#L48-L48"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Instr.Z\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">URM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Instr</span>.<span class=\"name\">Z</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a> → <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Instr\">Instr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Instr.Z","kind":"ctor","line":47,"name":"Cslib.URM.Instr.Z","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.lean#L47-L47"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_withi